#ASKYOURPDF
# ğŸ“„ PDF-RAG Platform (Gemini + Next.js + Qdrant + Clerk)

A full-stack AI-powered PDF processing platform that allows users to upload PDF documents, generate semantic embeddings using **Gemini-1.5-Flash**, and store them in a **Qdrant** vector database. Users authenticate securely using **Clerk**, and all uploads are queued and processed using **BullMQ**.

---

## ğŸ”§ Tech Stack

### ğŸ§  Backend
- **Node.js**, **Express**, **BullMQ** â€“ PDF processing and job queueing
- **LangChain.js** â€“ For document parsing and vector store support
- **Gemini 1.5 Flash (Google AI)** â€“ Embedding model
- **Qdrant** â€“ Vector database for semantic search
- **Redis** â€“ Queue broker

### ğŸŒ Frontend
- **Next.js 14** â€“ React framework
- **Clerk** â€“ User authentication and session management
- **Tailwind CSS** â€“ UI styling
- **Axios** â€“ For API communication

