## ğŸš€ Features

- âœ… Secure PDF upload with Clerk-authenticated users
- ğŸ¤– Background PDF parsing and embedding generation via Gemini
- ğŸ§  Semantic vector storage in Qdrant
- ğŸ“¦ Worker queue using BullMQ with Redis
